  "name": "Morrison COU1 — FDA generic centrifugal pump hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-1 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. All 13 credibility factors assessed with achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed across all operating points. Decision: Accepted.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-absolute-threshold",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cfd-hemolysis-below-clinical-threshold",
