      "rationale": "CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R2) operates under ISO 9001:2015 QMS. Version control via Git with tagged release 23.2.0. Regression test suite of 847 cases executed; all pass within tolerance. Software validation report SQA-2023-047 on file.",
