      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to the Navier-Stokes solver and scalar hemolysis transport equation. Observed order of convergence 1.92 (second-order scheme, theoretical 2.0); deviation within acceptable tolerance. Taylor-Green vortex benchmark confirms turbulence model implementation. Code verification report CVR-2024-003.",
