      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions documented in FDA benchmark protocol (CDRH-2012-BP). Temperature controlled to 37 ± 0.5 °C; haematocrit 40 ± 1%; flow rate measured with Coriolis meter (±0.5% FS). Pump speed measured with optical tachometer (±5 RPM). All boundary conditions in CFD model set to measured experimental values with uncertainty bounds propagated through UQ ensemble.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
