        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "QoI relevance acceptance criteria — Gradation 3",
        "description": "Primary QoI must be directly traceable to the regulatory acceptance criterion (NIH below clinical threshold). Mechanistic linkage between all computed QoIs and the clinical decision must be documented. QoI traceability matrix must be on file."
      }
