      "rationale": "Validation experiments performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump — geometrically identical to the device COU. Operating points in validation set span the full COU operating envelope (2.5–6.0 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Blood analogue (glycerol-water, matched viscosity) used in experiments; Soret-effect correction applied for temperature deviation. Validation relevance assessment documented in VRA-2025-005.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
