      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence monitored via normalised residuals (all < 10⁻⁵) and NIH monitor point stabilisation (< 0.1% change over final 500 iterations). Double-precision arithmetic used throughout. Round-off error estimated via interval arithmetic to be negligible (< 0.01% of NIH). Solver settings documented in simulation configuration file SCF-2025-003.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
