      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by independent CFD analyst (peer review checklist PR-2025-008). Boundary condition assignment, material property inputs, and solver settings verified against documented simulation plan SP-2025-001. Checklist covers 42 setup items; all items confirmed correct. User training records on file for all analysts involved.",
