      "rationale": "All model inputs (fluid density, viscosity, power-law coefficients C and α, pump geometry) sourced from peer-reviewed literature or direct measurement with traceable calibration certificates. Input uncertainty distributions characterised as normal or uniform based on measurement repeatability data. Input uncertainty propagated through 5000-sample Monte Carlo ensemble. Input data sheet IDS-2025-004 on file.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
