      "rationale": "Experimental dataset comprises n=5 independent repeat measurements at each of 5 operating points (25 total observations). Sample-to-sample variability characterised; coefficient of variation in NIH across repeats < 4.5% at all operating points. Sample size sufficient to estimate mean NIH with 95% CI half-width < 8% of mean. Sampling protocol documented in experimental report ER-2024-012.",
