      "rationale": "CFD boundary conditions set to experimentally measured values (flow rate, rotational speed, inlet pressure) with uncertainty bounds. Fluid rheology in CFD matched to experimental blood analogue via Carreau-Yasuda fit (R²=0.998). Geometric fidelity confirmed by CMM measurement of physical pump versus CAD model (max deviation 0.08 mm). Equivalency assessment documented in EIA-2025-006.",
